fail_loc=0
fake write 632.563274817 vs. normal write 543.527018226 in seconds
 sanity test_399: @@@@@@ FAIL: fake write is slower 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
